== AKAMARO ==
uretse kuba imigwegwe ikorwamo ibikorwa byinshi bifitiye igihugu nabaturage akamaro mu [[Rwanda]] hari amashyirahamwe

menshi yabagore bibumbiye hamwe bakabyaza umusaruro imigano murwego rwo kwiteza imbere babohamo uduseke two

kohereza mumahanga bakadutakisha amarange kugirango turusheho gusa neza abandi bakabohamo imitako ndetse nibindi

bikaba byarabafashije haba abo [[Umujyi wa Kigali|mu mujyi wa Kigali]] ndetse no muntara zitandukanye zo mu [[Rwanda]].

zibyo gusa kandi hari nabimwe mu bindi bihugu byavumbuye ko imigwegwe ikorwamo amoko yinzoga atandukanye nko muri [[Mexico]]<ref>https://glosbe.com/en/rw/agave</ref>

